---
export const prerender = true;
---
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Punto di Vista — Cultura, Tecnologia, Storie</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Noise overlay -->
  <div class="noise"></div>

  <!-- Back button -->
  <a href="/dev/portfolio" class="back-btn">
    <span class="back-arrow">&larr;</span> Torna al Portfolio
  </a>

  <!-- Breaking news ticker -->
  <div class="ticker">
    <div class="ticker-label">ULTIME NOTIZIE</div>
    <div class="ticker-track">
      <div class="ticker-content">
        <span>Biblioteche pubbliche: il ritorno come spazi di comunit&agrave;</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Cinque borghi italiani dove il tempo si &egrave; fermato</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Intervista: lo chef che ha lasciato la stella Michelin per tornare al paese</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Sei mesi nell'Artico: il diario di una ricercatrice italiana</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Biblioteche pubbliche: il ritorno come spazi di comunit&agrave;</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Cinque borghi italiani dove il tempo si &egrave; fermato</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Intervista: lo chef che ha lasciato la stella Michelin per tornare al paese</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
        <span>Sei mesi nell'Artico: il diario di una ricercatrice italiana</span>
        <span class="ticker-dot"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <header class="hero fade-in">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <div class="hero-category">Longform</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Il ritorno delle biblioteche pubbliche come spazi di comunit&agrave;</h1>
        <p class="hero-excerpt">
          Da Milano a Palermo, le biblioteche stanno diventando molto pi&ugrave; di depositi di libri:
          coworking, laboratori digitali, luoghi di incontro tra generazioni. Un viaggio nel cambiamento silenzioso
          che sta ridefinendo lo spazio pubblico italiano.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-meta">
          <span class="hero-author">di <strong>Chiara Ferrante</strong></span>
          <span class="hero-date">18 Marzo 2026</span>
          <span class="hero-read">14 min lettura</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/blog-hero.jpg" alt="Foto di copertina" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Categories -->
  <nav class="categories fade-in">
    <div class="categories-inner">
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill active">Tutti</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Tecnologia</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Cultura</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Economia</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Scienza</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Opinioni</a>
      <a href="#" class="cat-pill">Longform</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Main content -->
  <main class="content">
    <div class="content-inner">
      <!-- Articles grid -->
      <div class="articles">
        <article class="card card-featured fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="/images/portfolio/blog-typing.jpg" alt="Borghi italiani" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
            <div class="card-category-badge">Cultura</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="card-title">Cinque borghi italiani dove il tempo si &egrave; fermato</h2>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Da Civita di Bagnoregio a Castelmezzano, un viaggio tra i borghi dove la modernit&agrave; non &egrave; ancora arrivata &mdash; e forse non dovrebbe. Storie di resistenza, bellezza e comunit&agrave; che scelgono la lentezza.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Alessandra Ferraro</span>
              <span class="card-time">11 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <div style="width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a2e 0%,#16213e 50%,#0f3460 100%);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><span style="color:#a0aec0;font-size:2rem;">✍️</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Tecnologia</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Come l'intelligenza artificiale sta cambiando il giornalismo locale</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Redazioni con due giornalisti usano l'AI per coprire consigli comunali, cronaca e sport. Opportunit&agrave; reale o rischio per la professione?</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Luca Manzoni</span>
              <span class="card-time">8 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="/images/portfolio/blog-notebook.jpg" alt="Chef intervista" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Cultura</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Intervista: lo chef che ha lasciato la stella Michelin per tornare al paese</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Matteo Ferraris aveva tutto: una stella, il ristorante a Milano, la lista d'attesa. Poi ha scelto di tornare a cucinare nel borgo dove &egrave; nato. Ecco perch&eacute;.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Giulia Moretti</span>
              <span class="card-time">9 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="/images/portfolio/blog-books.jpg" alt="Ricercatrice artica" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Scienza</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Sei mesi nell'Artico: diario di una ricercatrice italiana</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Temperatura media: -32&deg;C. Sole assente per 67 giorni. Elena Ferraris racconta la sua missione scientifica alle Svalbard, tra ghiacci che si ritirano e scoperte inattese.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Elena Ferraris</span>
              <span class="card-time">18 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="/images/portfolio/blog-meeting.jpg" alt="Software libero" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Tecnologia</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Il codice sorgente della democrazia: software libero e partecipazione</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Comuni che pubblicano il codice delle piattaforme di voto, regioni che adottano Linux. Il software libero entra nelle istituzioni italiane.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Roberto Ferretti</span>
              <span class="card-time">7 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Pull Quote -->
        <blockquote class="pull-quote fade-in">
          <div class="pull-quote-mark">&ldquo;</div>
          <p>Non servono grandi budget per fare buon giornalismo. Servono curiosit&agrave;, rigore e il coraggio di raccontare anche le storie scomode.</p>
          <cite>&mdash; Maria Grazia Ferrante, direttrice editoriale di Punto di Vista</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <article class="card fade-in">
          <div class="card-image">
            <img src="/images/portfolio/blog-landscape.jpg" alt="Biblioteche come comunit&agrave;" loading="lazy" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="card-category-tag">Longform</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Il ritorno delle biblioteche pubbliche come spazi di comunit&agrave;</h3>
            <p class="card-excerpt">Coworking, fablab, sale prove musicali: le biblioteche italiane si reinventano. Un'inchiesta in cinque citt&agrave; su come lo spazio pubblico sta cambiando volto.</p>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <span class="card-author">Chiara Ferrante</span>
              <span class="card-time">14 min</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-sticky">
          <div class="sidebar-section glass-card fade-in">
            <h4 class="sidebar-title">Più Letti</h4>
            <ol class="most-read">
              <li>
                <span class="most-read-num">01</span>
                <a href="#">L'algoritmo che prevede le crisi economiche con 6 mesi di anticipo</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="most-read-num">02</span>
                <a href="#">Vivere senza smartphone: l'esperimento che ha cambiato la mia vita</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="most-read-num">03</span>
                <a href="#">Roma 2030: il piano urbanistico che divide gli esperti</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="most-read-num">04</span>
                <a href="#">Perché i giovani italiani tornano dai borghi</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="most-read-num">05</span>
                <a href="#">L'ultimo treno per la transizione energetica</a>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-section glass-card fade-in">
            <h4 class="sidebar-title">Newsletter</h4>
            <p class="sidebar-text">Ogni venerd&igrave; nella tua casella. Niente spam, solo le storie che contano. 4.200 lettori.</p>
            <form class="newsletter-form">
              <input type="email" placeholder="La tua email" class="newsletter-input" />
              <button type="button" class="newsletter-btn">Iscriviti</button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-section glass-card fade-in">
            <h4 class="sidebar-title">Tag Popolari</h4>
            <div class="tag-cloud">
              <a href="#" class="tag">Intelligenza Artificiale</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Clima</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Startup</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Europa</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Design</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Innovazione</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Sostenibilità</a>
              <a href="#" class="tag">Cultura</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Floating decorations -->
  <div class="floating-circle c1"></div>
  <div class="floating-circle c2"></div>
  <div class="floating-circle c3"></div>

  <footer class="footer fade-in">
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <h3>Punto di Vista</h3>
        <p>Cultura, tecnologia e storie dal mondo reale.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="#">Redazione</a>
        <a href="#">Chi siamo</a>
        <a href="#">Pubblicit&agrave;</a>
        <a href="#">Contatti</a>
        <a href="#">Privacy</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 Punto di Vista &mdash; Testata registrata al Tribunale di Milano n. 245/2020 &mdash; P.IVA 09876543210 &mdash; redazione@puntodivistamagazine.it</div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script is:inline>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          const el = entry.target;
          const delay = el.dataset.delay || 0;
          setTimeout(() => el.classList.add('visible'), Number(delay));
          observer.unobserve(el);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1 });

    document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach((el, i) => {
      el.dataset.delay = (i % 5) * 100;
      observer.observe(el);
    });

    // ===== CATEGORY FILTER =====
    document.querySelectorAll('.cat-pill').forEach(pill => {
      pill.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        document.querySelectorAll('.cat-pill').forEach(p => p.classList.remove('active'));
        pill.classList.add('active');
        const cat = pill.textContent.trim();
        document.querySelectorAll('.article-card, .grid-card').forEach(card => {
          const tag = card.querySelector('.card-category-tag, .card-category-badge');
          const match = cat === 'Tutti' || (tag && tag.textContent.trim() === cat);
          card.style.opacity = match ? '1' : '0.25';
          card.style.transform = match ? '' : 'scale(0.97)';
          card.style.transition = 'opacity 0.3s, transform 0.3s';
        });
      });
    });

    // ===== ARTICLE CLICK =====
    document.querySelectorAll('.article-card, .grid-card').forEach(card => {
      card.style.cursor = 'pointer';
      card.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const title = card.querySelector('h2, h3')?.textContent?.trim() || 'Articolo';
        showBlogToast('📖 Aprendo: ' + title.substring(0, 40) + '...');
      });
    });

    // ===== NEWSLETTER =====
    document.querySelector('.newsletter-btn')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const input = document.querySelector('.newsletter-input');
      if (!input?.value) { showBlogToast('Inserisci la tua email'); return; }
      input.value = '';
      showBlogToast('✓ Iscritto! Benvenuto nella community di Punto di Vista.');
    });

    // ===== TOAST =====
    let blogToastTimeout;
    function showBlogToast(msg) {
      const t = document.getElementById('blog-toast');
      t.textContent = msg;
      t.classList.add('show');
      clearTimeout(blogToastTimeout);
      blogToastTimeout = setTimeout(() => t.classList.remove('show'), 3200);
    }
  </script>

  <div id="blog-toast" style="position:fixed;bottom:28px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(80px);background:#1a1a1a;border:1px solid #dc2626;color:#fca5a5;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:50px;font-size:0.84rem;z-index:99999;opacity:0;transition:all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);white-space:nowrap;pointer-events:none;"></div>
  <style>#blog-toast.show{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}</style>

  <style>
    /* ===== RESET & BASE ===== */
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Source Sans 3', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* Custom scrollbar */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #f5f5f5; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #dc2626; border-radius: 4px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #b91c1c; }

    /* Noise overlay */
    .noise {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9999;
      opacity: 0.03;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      background-repeat: repeat;
      background-size: 256px 256px;
    }

    /* Fade-in animation */
    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }
    .fade-in.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* Floating circles */
    .floating-circle {
      position: fixed;
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
      opacity: 0.05;
      background: #dc2626;
    }
    .c1 { width: 400px; height: 400px; top: 10%; right: -100px; animation: floatA 20s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .c2 { width: 250px; height: 250px; bottom: 20%; left: -80px; animation: floatB 25s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .c3 { width: 150px; height: 150px; top: 60%; right: 10%; animation: floatA 18s ease-in-out infinite reverse; }
    @keyframes floatA {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
      33% { transform: translate(30px, -20px) scale(1.05); }
      66% { transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.95); }
    }
    @keyframes floatB {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
      50% { transform: translate(40px, -30px); }
    }

    /* ===== BACK BUTTON ===== */
    .back-btn {
      position: fixed;
      top: 58px;
      left: 20px;
      z-index: 1000;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(220,38,38,0.2);
      border-radius: 50px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    }
    .back-btn:hover {
      background: #dc2626;
      color: #fff;
      border-color: #dc2626;
      transform: translateX(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 25px rgba(220,38,38,0.25);
    }
    .back-arrow { font-size: 1.1rem; transition: transform 0.3s ease; }
    .back-btn:hover .back-arrow { transform: translateX(-3px); }

    /* ===== TICKER ===== */
    .ticker {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 999;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      height: 40px;
      background: #dc2626;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .ticker-label {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      padding: 0 20px;
      background: #1a1a1a;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    }
    .ticker-track { flex: 1; overflow: hidden; }
    .ticker-content {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 30px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      animation: ticker 40s linear infinite;
    }
    .ticker-dot {
      width: 5px; height: 5px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    @keyframes ticker {
      0% { transform: translateX(0); }
      100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    /* ===== HERO ===== */
    .hero { margin-top: 40px; padding: 80px 5vw 60px; }
    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-category {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: #dc2626;
      border: 1.5px solid #dc2626;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Merriweather', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #dc2626 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero-excerpt {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .hero-meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #888;
    }
    .hero-meta strong { color: #1a1a1a; }
    .hero-image {
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .hero-image img {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 4/3;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }
    .hero-image-lines {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      opacity: 0.15;
    }
    .hero-image-lines div {
      width: 60%; height: 3px;
      background: #aaa;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    /* ===== CATEGORIES ===== */
    .categories { padding: 0 5vw; margin-bottom: 50px; }
    .categories-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .cat-pill {
      padding: 8px 22px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #666;
      background: #f7f7f7;
      border: 1.5px solid transparent;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cat-pill:hover, .cat-pill.active {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626, #ef4444);
      color: #fff;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220,38,38,0.3);
    }

    /* ===== MAIN CONTENT ===== */
    .content { padding: 0 5vw 80px; }
    .content-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
      gap: 50px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .articles {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    /* ===== CARDS ===== */
    .card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
